      <p>The tool storage market is crowded. From entry-level plastic totes to premium rolling work stations, the choices can be paralysing — especially when you're spending your own hard-earned money on equipment that needs to survive a job site.</p>
      <p>We've evaluated the top tool boxes across every category — chests, modular systems, truck boxes, totes, and rolling stations — based on capacity, build quality, portability, security, and real-world ratings from professional tradespeople. Here's our complete comparison.</p>

